io.spine.js.generate.output.snippet

Class Import

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.spine.js.generate.output.CodeLine
      • io.spine.js.generate.output.snippet.Import

  • public class Import
extends CodeLine
    An import of a file or a library.

    The import is anonymous, but can be transformed into a named one.
